<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Alpinestars KR-HR on Lobotourisme</title><link>https://loboto51.github.io/lobotourisme/tags/alpinestars-kr-hr/</link><description>Lobotourisme (Alpinestars KR-HR)</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>fr-FR</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://loboto51.github.io/lobotourisme/tags/alpinestars-kr-hr/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Protections moto hanches Alpinestars Nucleon Racing KR-HR et Nucleon KR-H</title><link>https://loboto51.github.io/lobotourisme/post/protections-moto-hanches-alpinestars-nucleon-racing-kr-hr-et-nucleon-kr-h/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://loboto51.github.io/lobotourisme/post/protections-moto-hanches-alpinestars-nucleon-racing-kr-hr-et-nucleon-kr-h/</guid><description>&lt;p>Cette fiche récapitule les informations que j&amp;rsquo;ai pu glaner sur le net sur les coques de protection de hanches &lt;em>Alpinestars Nucleon Racing KR-HR et Nucleon KR-H&lt;/em> de niveau 1 et 2.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="alpinestars-nucleon-racing-hr-kr_HB_niv2_face__source_revzilla.jpg" alt="alpinestars-nucleon-racing-hr-kr_HB_niv2_face__source_revzilla.jpg">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>Synthèse :&lt;/em> Grande couverture, aération correcte, tarif élevé.&lt;/p>
